-- Spurs Defeat Thunder to Lead NBA Western Conference Finals 2
-- B y   D e x   M c L u s k e y
-- 2012-05-30T03:47:09Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-30/spurs-defeat-thunder-to-lead-nba-western-conference-finals-2.html
The  San Antonio Spurs  defeated the
Oklahoma City Thunder 120-111 to lead their National Basketball
Association playoff series by two games to none.  The winner of the Western Conference Finals will play the
Miami Heat or Boston Celtics in the NBA Finals. That series
resumes tomorrow in Miami with the Heat leading 1-0.  After two games in San Antonio, the Thunder host the Spurs
in Game 3 of the best-of-seven series on May 31 and again, two
days later.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Dex McLuskey at 
 dmcluskey@bloomberg.net  